<P>
Photo, Maurice, Carolyn DeWald at their Pacific Palisades home. He heads Music 
Center Unified Fund drive; she co-chairs Bunker Hill Steps inaugural benefit 
for Maguire Thomas Partners and the Music Center. ALEX BERLINER / For The Times 
</P>
