<P>
St Bonaventure 13, Calabasas 6 -- St. Bonaventure quarterback Peter Houston 
connected with Rudy Camacho on a 35-yard scoring pass and Jose Payan scored on 
a one-yard run in a nonleague game at Calabasas (1-3). 
</P>
<P>
St. Bonaventure (2-2) added a touchdown in the third quarter to take a 13-0 
advantage. Calabasas' only score came in the fourth quarter when Damon Riggins, 
who rushed for 52 yards in 17 carries, recovered a fumble and ran 48 yards for 
a score. J. SCOTT KLEIN 
