<P>
Clarice A. Blamer 
</P>
<P>
Age: 68 
</P>
<P>
Occupation: Incumbent/ retired teacher. 
</P>
<P>
Background: Has served on council for eight years. Was mayor for 18 months. 
Serves on the Orange County Transportation Commission, the county Congestion 
Management Plan Committee and the AQMD's Air Quality Plan Implementing 
Committee. Taught math and biology for 26 years in the Fullerton Union High 
School District. 
